  <name>sfTitleMakerPlugin</name>
  <channel>pear.symfony-project.com</channel>
  <summary>
    Provides an easy to use way of managing HTML hierachical title
    segments separated by a delimiter.
  </summary>
  <description>
    The `sfTitleMakerPlugin` allows you to create modular/hierachical content
    to be passed to the html `title` tag.

    Examples:

    1. My Website » News » Hungry man eats horse
    2. Royal Blue Egg Cup | Ceramics | Products | My Online Store
  </description>
